# ReadU environment variables
#
# Add your Anthropic API key to enable LIVE, AI-personalized passage generation
# (Claude writes a brand-new passage + questions tuned to the reader's interests,
# level, and weakest skills on every session).
#
# Without a key, ReadU still works end-to-end using its built-in, pre-generated
# content library — great for offline demos.
#
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com  →  copy this file to `.env.local`.

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here
